## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Fix |
| ------- | ---- |
| Assets load from `localhost:5173` in production build | `rm public/hot` and rebuild (`npm run build`) |
| Code changes not reflected | `docker compose restart app` (Octane keeps code in memory) |
| Permission errors on `storage/` | `docker compose exec app chmod -R ugo+rw storage bootstrap/cache` |
| `migrate`/`db:seed` refuse to run | `APP_ENV=production` requires `--force`, or set `APP_ENV=local` |

